{
  "texts": [
    "Thirdly, there currently is a lack of test types in ILAP.",
    "We are working on implementing more test types, which would make the platform more versatile and adaptable to more use cases.",
    "Additionally, the system could provide even more support in the item creation process, for instance an assessment of an item's difficulty.",
    "This functionality is currently not integrated into the platform.",
    "Arguably, this would make it easier to create EIT items of varying difficulty."
  ]
}